Text:
...Nothing against Delta's extreme attack power,
but her claws won't work as effectively in some
scenarios.
Delta. Try using your slime sword.
Why? I can hunt without it!

That's precisely why it's an excellent opportunity to
give it a go. Try engaging in a fight with three or
more opponents. Think you can handle it?
...Fine! I'll give it a try!
Grrraaaarrrr!!!

Delta. You might want to use something a little more
compact—

If I'm gonna take them out together, the bigger the
sword, the better!
Well—
Swoooooshhh!!!
Aaaaaghhhh!!!

Delta's current fighting style doesn't resemble
Shadow's swordsmanship in any shape or form.

But this should give her an opportunity to experience
the versatility and usefulness of a sword firsthand.
Huraaaaaaahhh!!!
Gyaaaargghhhh!!!
Oooohhh!

Lady Alpha! Swords are actually pretty cool! Makes it
easier to hunt a bunch of them at the same time!

...At least that's the idea. But she's wielding it
more as an iron blob than a sword.
Well, I guess it'll do for now.
There's no way we're beating this beast! Fall back!
Fall back to where, sir?
Back to the cave, you idiot!
But the bird is in there—

I'll take my chances with the bird over this monster
any day! Besides, if we're lucky, maybe they'll kill
each other.
If you run, I'll hunt you down!
Agghhh!
Ahh...!

You should've spent more time running instead of
talking.
Grarrr... One left to go!
Delta. Wait.
Wait...?!

This one seems to know a thing or two. I'd like to
talk to him first.
There's nothing to talk about! Kill the weakling!
Delta.
Eeek...!
Eep...!
What're you getting scared for?!
W-Well...you're pretty terrifying...!

Then you'd best stay on my good side by answering my
questions.
What...! You mean you'll spare my life?
That all depends on you.

Well, no matter what you say, you'll end up dead
anyway!
Wha—?!
Delta?!

I'm not wrong, am I? We always finish them off once
we get them to talk!

Besides, the intel they give us is usually useless
anyway. It's faster to just kill him now...
*sigh*
Wait a minute! Then I'm dead either way!

I don't know who you people are, but how could you
kill someone in cold blood without a second thought?!

A Cult of Diablos scum like you lecturing me on
morality? You're really starting to anger me!

Considering what you bastards are doing to the
possessed children, killing you would be too
kind a fate.

What! How the hell do you know about the Cult and the
possessed?! Who are you people...? Wait, were you the
ones who attacked the hideout in the Sacred Land?!
You really don't know?! We're the—
Zip it!
Eek!

Delta. As one-sided as this is, it's still a
"negotiation."

We're supposed to gain useful intel, not
inadvertently give the other party intel
on us.
F-Fine...!
Um...let's see...

Gimme intel! Or I kill you now! If you gimme intel,
I'll kill you later!
That's not called "negotiating"...
If I'm dead whether I talk or not, then—!
Then? Then what?

...Looks like it was lured here by the scent of
blood.
I-I may have a chance—
Gyahhhh!!!

Heyyy! It ate my prey! You sneaky bird! How dare you
steal from me!
Fine... You're my next prey!
